The paper proposes a novel approach to modeling cognitive events from EEG data using deep neural networks, specifically convolutional neural networks (CNN) and recurrent neural networks (RNN). This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
